{"tid":2124782,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"教育局：學生在校內或校外均不應戴上口罩","createTime":"2020-07-25T15:59:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T16:35:38.000Z","uid":216992,"like":43,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"553115615ddabfe95b8155bba33192b8cd2a3ef8","tid":2124782,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T15:59:33.000Z","msg":"2019-10-5<br />\n<br />\n教育局向全港學校校監及校長發信，標題為「《禁止蒙面規例》在2019年10月5日起生效」，信中指出因應《禁蒙面法》在午夜後生效，促請學校提醒學生及家長，為免誤墮法網，學生外出時不要以任何方式遮蓋臉孔。<br />\n<br />\n「<span class=\"red\">原則上，學生在校內或校外均不應戴上口罩</span>或以任何其他方式遮蓋臉孔，宗教或健康原因除外，如學生或教職員身體不適，最佳做法是盡早求醫及留在家中休息。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2019-10-12<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄指出，規例雖然不適用於校園，惟<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">學生在校內戴口罩畢竟是某種表達訴求方法</span></span>，擔心會迫使其他同學表態，<span class=\"red\">令學校運作變得複雜</span>。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/articlePrint/id/2274210\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2FarticlePrint%2Fid%2F2274210&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHQ9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=169e77ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/articlePrint/id/2274210</a>"},{"pid":"05b7d1d03d2cc8d74e4c977fb1a01a6f9dcac956","tid":2124782,"uid":216992,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T16:00:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />停課前好多學生都戴口罩返學 幾時拉人"},{"pid":"754cb2f571edb7134f1a1db24483ef235c68dfb3","tid":2124782,"uid":38904,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T16:00:34.000Z","msg":"學生:<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-CahYsoGunHM/XX8R78nVX3I/AAAAAAAAg00/NGBTz5_u730iyDcyGg3yJsPI0mg05dvmwCNcBGAsYHQ/s320/AmIJoke.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-CahYsoGunHM%2FXX8R78nVX3I%2FAAAAAAAAg00%2FNGBTz5_u730iyDcyGg3yJsPI0mg05dvmwCNcBGAsYHQ%2Fs320%2FAmIJoke.jpg&h=0d93aa1e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8823bf336143e452c2254c3b35cb